## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible strategies employed by different healthcare facilities. Additionally, the information is limited to what is publicly accessible and may not reflect the most current practices in all settings. The search was also constrained by the availability of full-text articles and the specificity of the search terms used.